info.description:
Complete CRUD for Book and BookVariant APIs.

All file uploads go through Cloudinary automatically.
Duration for audio/video is auto-calculated on server — no need to send it.

Response format:
- Success: { data: {...} }
- Error: { error: "message" }

GET responses return populated objects:
- categories: [{ _id, name, imageUrl, description }]
- donorId: { _id, name, email }
- formats[].donorId: { _id, name, email }

request.description:
Returns all non-deleted books with:
- categories: populated objects with { _id, name, imageUrl, description }
- variants: array of BookVariant documents with populated donor info
- variants[].donorId: { _id, name, email }
- variants[].formats[].donorId: { _id, name, email }

